\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">2. Financial Analysis &amp; Reporting</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Financial statements (balance sheet, income statement, cash flow statement)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Ratio analysis (liquidity, profitability, solvency)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Common-size and trend analysis</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">3. Capital Budgeting &amp; Investment Decisions</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Net Present Value (NPV), Internal Rate of Return (IRR), Payback Period</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Risk analysis in capital budgeting</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Cost of capital (WACC)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">4. Working Capital Management</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l7 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Cash, inventory, and receivables management</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l7 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Short-term financing strategies</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l7 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Operating cycle and cash conversion cycle</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">5. Risk Management &amp; Derivatives</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l6 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Types of financial risks (market, credit, operational)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l6 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Hedging strategies (futures, options, swaps)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l6 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Insurance and diversification</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">6. Corporate Finance</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo6; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Capital structure (debt vs. equity)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo6; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Dividend policy and share buybacks</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo6; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Mergers &amp; acquisitions (M&amp;A)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">7. International Financial Management</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l8 level1 lfo7; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Foreign exchange risk</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l8 level1 lfo7; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Cross-border investment</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l8 level1 lfo7; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Global capital markets</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">8. Behavioral Finance</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l5 level1 lfo8; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Psychological biases in financial decision-making</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l5 level1 lfo8; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Market anomalies</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-s