(231, '821300', 692, 'ABC Hospitality Training Center', 'storage/certificates/logos/6825a36e4cd55.download-removebg-preview.png', 'storage/certificates/images/687224dc60e6a.1736057277.png', '<p>This official student identification card is issued by <strong>ABC Hospitality Training Center </strong>to <strong>Aung Aung. </strong>It certifies active student status and grants access to campus facilities valid till December 2025.</p>', '<p><strong>Course Outlines</strong><br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Customer Service<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Restaurant Services<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Fundamentals of the Hotel &amp; Catering Industry<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Housekeeping &amp; Accommodation Studies<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Food &amp; Beverage Management<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Front Office Operations &amp; Administration<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Strategic Management in Hospitality<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Organizational Behavior &amp; Hospitality Management<br>&bull; &nbsp; &nbsp;Environmental Management in the Hospitality Industry</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Course Objectives:</strong><br>Upon completion of this program, participants will be able to:<br>1) &nbsp; &nbsp;Deliver Effective Customer Service: Provide high-quality service and resolve customer issues.<br>2) &nbsp; &nbsp;Manage Restaurant Operations: Execute efficient restaurant service and manage related tasks.<br>3) &nbsp; &nbsp;Understand Hotel &amp; Catering Fundamentals: Grasp core concepts of the hospitality industry.<br>4) &nbsp; &nbsp;Apply Housekeeping &amp; Accommodation Standards: Maintain high standards for guest accommodations.<br>5) &nbsp; &nbsp;Manage Food &amp; Beverage Services: Control costs and optimize food and beverage operations.<br>6) &nbsp; &nbsp;Administer Front Office Procedures: Handle guest services and front desk tasks.<br>7) &nbsp; &nbsp;Implement Hospitality Strategic Management: Develop and apply strategic plans.<br>8) &nbsp; &nbsp;Analyze Hospitality Organizational Behavior: Understand team dynamics an